reviews.title: Love update
reviews.comment: I\'m enjoying the updates I appreciate that now I can deposit my checks directly through my phone. I deposited a check mobile Friday at about 5:30 funds where available within the next couple of hours.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: About time!!
reviews.comment: Love the text notices when you get deposits and withdrawals. But its lacking check deposit feature..which is a BIG must!!!. Once it gets that feature and transfer to other banks. It will get 5 stars   Edit 08/21/13..Woot about time check deposit came
reviews.author: Ann Allen

reviews.title: Love it
reviews.comment: Perfect application love the updates...
reviews.author: Tranitta Levels

reviews.title: Love mobile deposit, but...
reviews.comment: I am in love with mobile deposit and with the fact that it\'s instant! However, now we need to be able to transfer funds from our own account to someone else\'s, both within the credit union and at other banks. Also, I want to be able to use the message system via the app.
reviews.author: Rebecca Dittmar

reviews.title: Nice
reviews.comment: Love it
reviews.author: felicia johnson

reviews.title: Love this bank
reviews.comment: Great app to have to needing when u get paid or when ur broke
reviews.author: Tina Delacruz

reviews.title: 4 out of 5
reviews.comment: Still waiting to be able to have the ability to update profile throigh phone rather than computer. Like change my address. Great bank and app is good. Thanks sccu
reviews.author: Aaron Du Pont

reviews.title: Love SCCU
reviews.comment: Mobile deposit and Bill payer!!!
reviews.author: Carrie Roberts

reviews.comment: Love SCCU
reviews.author: Bobbi Thomas

reviews.title: Convenient app!
reviews.comment: I love this app but have been having trouble opening it for about a week now.
reviews.author: Melissa Mendenhall

reviews.title: Great update
reviews.comment: This update was needed. Great improvement on functionality of mobile app. Love it!
reviews.author: Luis Tomas

reviews.title: Slightly annoying
reviews.comment: Only allows you to register one account at a time on your device. Logging out of one account and into another is more complicated than it needs to be. Once you\'re inside the app everything looks nice and is easy to use.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Good soild start!
reviews.comment: YES!! Welcome to the app world SCCU!! This is a good soild start but sparse with functionality and directions. A BoA online banking style app is where I hope this ends up getting to after a few more update down the road but you\'re online and off to a good start so keep them updates coming!!!!
reviews.author: jeff cross

reviews.title: Dennis from Miami, FL
reviews.comment: Very convenient.. I would\'ve given this app a 5 star if it facilitated bill pay & an accessible way of obtaining your account # & back routing #
reviews.author: Dennis Haughton

reviews.title: It\'s a start!
reviews.comment: The app is incredibly convenient for transferring funds and checking balances.  The only thing I would like to see is the ability to deposit a check.
reviews.author: Brianne Linder

reviews.title: so far so good
reviews.comment: seems to be ok.  I guess we will really get a good bang for the buck when we can do some check deposits like other banking apps.  Right not not particularly useful for me unless we can add external accounts and do transfers and check deposits. 3 stars for now since I would want additional features.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Nice Basic Banking
reviews.comment: Finally an SCCU app! To repeat from an earlier review, moving between SCCU accounts is annoying as you have to deregister the device and reregister. We have three accounts, so imagine. Will also be happy to see the day when we finally get a mobile deposit capability which they are projecting in 2013.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great app!
reviews.comment: It even shows my pending transactions. Now I don\'t have to worry about calling in and asking them what is pending!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: So-so
reviews.comment: Definitely has something to be desired. You really can\'t do anything with this app other than view your account info & transfer funds. Any more than that you might as well log onto a PC.   The most valuable feature I wish to see in an upgrade is check cashing from my phone.  KUDOS in upgrading w/check deposits
reviews.author: Brock Woodward

reviews.title: The SCCU Mobile Banking App is Great!
reviews.comment: Fast and easy to check my SCCU accounts.  I can search for locations and set up security alerts.  This is great. I had the same problem with multiple sign ons. But I called SCCU and the folks there were able to join all my accounts to show under one signon!  Now I don\'t even have to sign in twice to see everything which is even better!
reviews.author: A Google User
